        <img src="https://media.dwnews.net/hk01/RmBZEDymORjTZe9-MxHvyMthcEY%3D/320*0/media/images/dw/20210827/507772564873940992705124.jpeg" alt="喀布尔机场外发生爆炸，现场异常惨烈。（AP）" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
